title: Duo Sladko Medeno [7CD Wav Edition] Bulgarian Folk Songs
description:
Bulgarian Folk Duet
Sladko Medeno
Favourite BG Folk Songs
Special Remastered Compilation

Duo gives new insight into Bulgarian folklore - and sound - and choice of instruments and arrangements. Heat and specificity. Sounds and harmonies of innovation, much different from past traditions in the Bulgarian style of recording and making music ... New voices and new artistry. New magic! Great compilation, meeting the requirements of time and a challenge to listeners, connoisseurs!

Master Folders:
1 DEVOIKO MARI HUBAVA
2 BRALA MOMA KAPINI
3 DRAGIEVA CHESHMA
4 HORA I RYCHENICI
5 ORIENTAL - KUCHECI
6 FAVOURITE BG FOLK DANCES - INSTRUMENTAL
7 SLADKO MEDENO - POP BALADS BY ANTOAN ANTONOV

Recording and everything concerning the processing of sound:
Dimitar Petrov
